fields.title: Linear Regression Exercise
fields.description: Practice implementing linear regression from scratch and using popular machine learning libraries.

fields.title: K-Means Clustering Exercise
fields.description: Explore the K-Means clustering algorithm and practice implementing it on various datasets.

fields.title: Convolutional Neural Networks Exercise
fields.description: Learn about convolutional neural networks and practice implementing them for image recognition tasks.

fields.title: Reinforcement Learning Exercise
fields.description: Implement and experiment with reinforcement learning algorithms, such as Q-learning and Deep Q-Networks, in various environments.

fields.title: Natural Language Processing Exercise
fields.description: Practice implementing various natural language processing techniques, such as sentiment analysis, named entity recognition, and text classification.

fields.title: Generative Adversarial Networks Exercise
fields.description: Implement generative adversarial networks (GANs) and experiment with generating realistic images, text, or other data types.

fields.title: Transfer Learning Exercise
fields.description: Learn about transfer learning and fine-tune pre-trained models to perform tasks, such as image classification and object detection.
